# Rules Engine Roadmap

Use this when continuing Phase 3 implementation.

## Milestone 1 — Done

- Formula evaluator, character/improvement models
- `ImprovementManager` + `ValueOf` + transactions
- Handlers: `addattribute`, `enabletab`, `specificattribute`, `conditionmonitor`, `damageresistance`, `armor`, `initiative`
- `deriveStats` (physical/stun CM, threshold, overflow)
- 15 Vitest tests passing

## Milestone 2 — Done

- Attribute total calculation (base + improvement min/max/aug)
- Handlers: `specificskill`, `skillcategory`, `drainresist`, `fadingresist`, `nuyenamt`, `livingpersona`, `initiativepass`
- `requirement-validator.ts` — `forbidden`/`required`/`oneof`/`allof`
- Golden tests from `qualities.json` / `metatypes.json` fixtures

## Milestone 3 — Done

- `bp-calculator.ts`, `nuyen-calculator.ts`, `availability-validator.ts`
- `metatype-initializer.ts`, `character-validator.ts`
