## Milestone 4 — Done

- `CharacterStoreService` (signals + computed derived stats, BP, nuyen, validation)
- Selection request protocol for interactive handlers (`selectattribute`, `selectskill`, `selecttext`, `selectskillgroup`)

## Milestone 5 — Done

- Creation tab shell with conditional tabs (Common, Skills, Magician, Adept, etc.)
- IndexedDB persistence via `CharacterStorageService`
- Legacy `.chum` import via `chum-importer.ts`

## Milestone 6 — Done

Finish the character foundation before skills and gear. Most of this extends existing models and the Common / Character Info tabs.

### Rules / models

- `CharacterSkill`, `CharacterSkillGroup`, `CharacterKnowledgeSkill` models (rating, specs, free/default flags)
- `skill-calculator.ts` — BP for active skills, skill groups, knowledge/language skills (uses `CharacterOptions.bp*`)
- Extend `calculateBp()` with skill and martial-arts line items
- Metavariant selection in `metatype-initializer.ts` (UI + data from `metatypes.json`)
- Special attribute editing: EDG, MAG, RES (respect metatype min/max and BP costs)
- Contacts BP already in `bp-calculator.ts`; wire `character.contacts` editing

### UI

- Metavariant picker on Common tab (per metatype, including “None”)
- Special attributes section on Common tab
- Contacts editor (connection / loyalty / group, enemy, free)
- Nuyen-for-BP slider or input (updates `nuyenBpSpent`, respects `getMaxNuyenBp()`)
- Replace **Character Info** placeholder with notes, sex/age/height/weight fields (persist on character)

### Persistence / import

- Extend `chum-importer.ts` for `<contacts>` and `<skills>` / `<skillgroups>` / knowledge skills
- Round-trip contacts and basic info in IndexedDB documents

### Tests

- Skill BP golden cases (default skill, raised skill, skill group, knowledge skill)
- Metavariant bundled qualities + BP
- Contact free-CH A refund logic

### Legacy reference

- `frmCreate.cs` — contact BP, nuyen BP, special attribute raises
- `clsCharacter.cs` — skill rating storage

### Done when

A Human with contacts, raised EDG, and a few default skills validates BP correctly and survives save/load.

